
compile the code by

  $make all

run the code with

  $./run "InputFile/run278240.txt" "run278240" "." "" "0"

The first argument is the input file that contains the address to the ntuples to be analyzed

the second argument is a text that will be used in naming the out put

the third argument is the output directory

the fourth argument is just an extra string that will be used in naming the output file

the last argument is verbosity


